node.text: ❤️50 miles in 5 days….. at “Karin’s Bootcamp” @karin_luter  It was time to reboot and attack the extra 20 COVID pounds and what better way then doing it with your best and most athletic friend….. thank you snooch for an incredible week, I love you, i appreciate you and treasure our 28 year friendship.  The hikes, the weight classes, massages, soups and salads where the perfect reset. You still make me laugh like nobody else, thank you for physically  challenging me but keeping up with your Norwegian speed is almost impossible 😜 Can’t wait to get home and hit the scale or rather try on my clothes that don’t fit……. It’s not about how I look to others but rather how I feel within myself #bootcamp #Aspen
